Title: Suki tte Nandarou... Namida
Description: ['Music video directed by ShiShi Yamazaki for the song ', Suki tte Nandarou... Namida, " by YUKI (Yuki Kuramochi). The full version of the music video was officially released on YouTube for a limited time before the single's drop on July 29, 2015. It was also included on DVD with a limited edition release."]
